metadata.name: Transformative Traditions
metadata.description: Transformative Traditions explores how traditional values and cultural practices change and evolve over time. Through a series of thought-provoking art pieces, the collection challenges viewers to question their assumptions about tradition and encourages them to consider how cultural norms can be transformed to better reflect contemporary values. From the preservation of cultural heritage to the creation of new traditions, this collection celebrates the power of art to inspire change and transformation.
